mods.abstract: This award was presented for outstanding achievement and service to Christian Brothers High School. The recipients for 1994-1995 were: Tim Dwyer, James Rodney Feild, E. Lee Giovannetti, John E. Harkins, Robert L. Kuehner, Eugene J. Podesta, Rev. Joseph L. Tagg, III, Jesse H. Turner, Jr., William F. Wolbrecht. Deceased inductees: John B. Mason, Jr., John S. Robilio, Sr.
